---
title: Red Thai Inspired Fish Curry with Peas and Jasmine Rice
description: Red chillies give Thai Red its signature colour, as well as its flavour and heat! Here, our Red Thai Inspired Fish Curry is loaded with salmon, cod and smoked haddock in a curried coconut milk base.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R28_W38_UK_R22354-4_Main_high-b8daa313.jpg
